Project Overview: The UCD AI Agent project is a chatbot-based automation tool designed to execute various system-level scripts and commands. Key features: Execute shell scripts like hello.sh and ansible.sh., Run Ansible playbooks for system automation., Fetch OS details and restart services., Interactive chatbot interface with predefined responses and spell correction., Speech synthesis for bot responses.
